  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class RequesterFragment
extends android.app.Fragment
    A simple Fragment subclass. Activities that contain this fragment must implement the RequestFeedFragment.OnFragmentInteractionListener interface to handle interaction events. Use the RequestFeedFragment.newInstance() factory method to create an instance of this fragment.
